annotationB: Guanosine-3',5'-bis(diphosphate) 3'-pyrophosphohydrolase MESH1; Metazoan SpoT homolog-1 is a structural and functional ortholog of bacterial protein SpoT. It hydrolyzes ppGpp to GDP.
